text = "Crumpitt sprints to General Griffin’s office for clarification on the situation, to know if it isn’t a simple exercise, only to find him incapacited on the floor.

“OH MY GIDDY AUNT!!! WHAT HAPPENED???”

Looking into the documents laying on the office’s desk, Crumpitt finds out that Griffin launched Wing Attack Plan Z, sending the bomb squad to move towards their targets in the Soviet Union. And the planes can’t be recalled without the five-letter secret code that can go through their discriminators.

Thankfully, the characters that compose that secret code can be retrieved in modified fax machines scattered around the base."
